{
  "stem": "18626.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 313.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The German, his friend, when he came in, he was angry like a lion, like a tiger.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had in his hand a leather strap like the German were, you know, where they beat people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't know who to cut and who to slice over the head, you know, with that strap, the way he was walking through.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the-- the yard in this-- in the-- in the factory like a monster.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That how angry he was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Wiedmann was just going with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't say a word, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then he came into my department right from the yard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We all looked through the window.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We saw the anger, and we all start to work right by the lathes, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Fast.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He's coming in, into our shops.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he walked in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We saw the anger on his face.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When he looked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then he walked by my lathe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At that time, I was turning a chess set from little bones.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it's called a pocket chess set.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's so small, the figures, that you put them in, you know, with little pins.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's turned on-- and each figure from the chess is turned on a small little pin, and in a little box with a chess set and you stick in and you play like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And you can keep in your pocket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "A beautiful job.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I turned the chess set.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he looked at the lathe, the way I turned.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the white shavings from the figures, you know, fall right on my lathe.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the way I shape it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he looked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And at that time, I was young, and I had very blond hair.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I mean, real blond.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
